{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XzdaHRtuiJcETzFmRtc7yY","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__roster__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/Dockerfile has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→FROM maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n     2→\n     3→USER root\n     4→# install uv\n     5→RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl python3-venv python3-full \\\n     6→    && curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n     7→\n     8→ENV PATH=\"/root/.local/bin:$PATH\"\n     9→\n    10→# create venv and install\n    11→RUN uv venv /opt/venv \\\n    12→    && uv pip install --python /opt/venv/bin/python pytest requests\n    13→\n    14→ENV PATH=\"/opt/venv/bin:$PATH\"\n    15→\n    16→# Set working directory\n    17→WORKDIR /app\n    18→\n    19→# Copy all the assets\n    20→COPY . .\n    21→\n    22→RUN if [ -f smoke.py ]; then chmod +x smoke.py; fi\n    23→\n    24→RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests\n    25→\n    26→EXPOSE 8080\n    27→\n    28→CMD [\"java\", \"-jar\", \"target/quarkus-app/quarkus-run.jar\"]\n    29→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40d6367f-f3fd-4de9-a25e-2a8ba1c4e96f","uuid":"4046650b-c4dd-4a99-8f7d-038c95a3ef2c"}
